Hi Team

We had a prototype launch before - got a bunch of user feedback
https://docs.google.com/document/d/16Ri9PeOR8AZYG4yLDv-svNXhabRAOTB2v2CFrDcKNBE/edit?tab=t.0 - take a read when free

I have made @jemin.jain @pauline.comising @Abhishek Adupa admins on aihub-sandbox. @ayesha.ali and @Weiming Wu already have admin accounts.
You should be able to access the apps referenced. You can find app metadata (like input dir/output dir) by MySQL querying in Grafana.
```SELECT * FROM instabase.job_metadata WHERE job_id=<>```
